OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FITV News North of England Reporter
OL,7,FJonathan Brown followed the progress
OL,8,Fof some of the 70 young people who put
OL,9,Fdown their phones
OL,11,FPupils at schools in Sheffield have
OL,12,Fgiven up their smartphones for three
OL,13,Fweeks after some admitted to using
OL,14,Fthem for up to 13 hours a day.
OL,16,FThe group, aged between four and 17,
OL,17,Fvolunteered to swap their devices for
OL,18,Fso-called 'brick phones' without
OL,19,Finternet or social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
