PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FIt comes as the government considers
OL,7,FAustralia-style plans to ban under-16s
OL,8,Fin the UK from social media platforms.
OL,10,FA consultation, which ends on May 26,
OL,11,Falso looks at restrictions on
OL,12,Faddictive features, including infinite
OL,13,Fscrolling, and better support for
OL,14,Fcaregivers to allow young people to be
OL,15,Fonline safely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
