FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FITV News followed the progress of some
OL,7,Fof the 70 young people who put down
OL,8,Ftheir phones - among them was Maliah
OL,9,FSibanda, 14, who says her algorithm
OL,10,Fhas thrown up violent and explicit
OL,11,Fcontent on social media.
OL,13,F"I'm on my phone for 13 hours a day,"
OL,14,Fshe said. "Even when I had my phone,
OL,15,FI'd just be thinking 'I could be doing
OL,16,Fso many more productive things right
OL,17,Fnow', and I'm sat scrolling through
OL,18,FTikTok. I'm on it until I fall asleep."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@eO]vD@KOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
