PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FStanley Sheldon, 14, used his phone
OL,7,Ffor six hours a day before the
OL,8,Fexperiment and relied on it to contact
OL,9,Fhis friends.
OL,11,FHe said: "If you lost it (your
OL,12,Fsmartphone), you'd lose quite a few
OL,13,Ffriends."
OL,15,FSpencer Kubon, 11, added: "You can get
OL,16,Fvery sucked in by it (social media).
OL,17,FSome people get it at a very young age
OL,18,Fand then they are just always on it."
OL,26,@sD@JOUuD@IO]wD@[OUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
