PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FThe three-week project was organised
OL,7,Fby staff at Ecclesfield School in
OL,8,FSheffield and featured its four feeder
OL,9,Fschools.
OL,11,FThe idea was first piloted at
OL,12,FEcclesfield last year, but the number
OL,13,Fof pupils who volunteered to take part
OL,14,Fthis year has more than doubled.
OL,16,F"Kids are falling out, and they might
OL,17,Fnot come in, they might be struggling
OL,18,Fwith their mental health because of
OL,19,Fthings that they are seeing online,"
OL,20,Fsaid Liz Hunter, the teacher behind
OL,21,Fthe initiative.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,F"Loads of children are surviving on
OL,7,Ffour to six hours sleep a night -
OL,8,Ftheir attention is shot.
OL,10,F"We need a rule about this (social
OL,11,Fmedia) for brains not fully developed
OL,12,Fto handle the power of these
OL,13,Fplatforms."
OL,15,FIn total, only three pupils dropped
OL,16,Fout of the smartphone swap project
OL,17,Fover the three weeks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
