PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FTeachers reported seeing students'
OL,7,Fsleep improve; some told them they
OL,8,Fwere spending more time with family or
OL,9,Fdoing activities, while others
OL,10,Freported struggles with boredom and
OL,11,Fsocial isolation.
OL,13,FBut for all those who took part, it
OL,14,Fmade them reflect on their screen
OL,15,Ftime, including parents who wish they
OL,16,Fhadn't introduced them so early and
OL,17,Fuse them to monitor their children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
