OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779487871
OL,3,CPupils swap smartphones for 'bricks'
OL,4,Cunder three-week project
OL,6,FNow with their phones back and
OL,7,Funlimited access to social media, we
OL,8,Fwill have to see if these devices are
OL,9,Fstill the first and last thing they
OL,10,Faccess each day.
